LayerVault,is,a,site,for,creative,professionals,that,provides,hosting,and,other,cloud,services,The,Designer,News,feature,of,the,site,provides,a,feed,of,the,top,design,related,stories,in,the,news,The,Designer,News,API,provides,tools,for,interacting,with,Designer,News,and,allowing,applications,to,access,user,information,The,API,uses,REST,calls,and,returns,JSON,For,authentication,the,API,uses,oAuth,and,SSL,An,account,is,required,with,service,and,usage,limits,are,defaulted,to,calls,per,hour